To install, add these lines to [[Special:MyPage/monobook.js|your personal javascript]]:

 import_script('User:Whiteknight/gadgetscore.js');
 import_script('User:Whiteknight/{{{1|gadgets.js}}}');

Your personal Javascript page is most likely located at "User:<YOUR USER NAME>/monobook.js" Go to that page and copy+paste the above line of code and click {{Key|name=Save Page}}. 

Once you save your javascript, you will need to perform a '''hard reset''', typically by pressing {{Key|name=Ctrl}} + {{Key|name=F5}}, or some other key combination.

